### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog

### Get service document (lists all entities in CatalogService)
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Authorization: Basic alice:alice


### Step A: Create a NEW DRAFT (not yet a real Book)
POST {{baseUrl}}/Books
Authorization: Basic alice:alice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Draft Book Example",
  "price": 30.00
}

### Step B: Read drafts only - this entity set is auto-generated by draft-enabling
GET {{baseUrl}}/Books/DraftAdministrativeData
Authorization: Basic alice:alice

### Step C: Activate the draft (turns it into a real, queryable Book)
### Replace ID with the draft's ID from Step A's response
POST {{baseUrl}}/Books(ID=c287680e-835e-475a-a0c9-efc07e676de6,IsActiveEntity=false)/draftActivate
Authorization: Basic alice:alice
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Step D: Confirm it now appears in normal active GET
GET {{baseUrl}}/Books
Authorization: Basic alice:alice